ain death (Spanish)|work=[[Lopez Doriga Digital]]| date=18 January 2017| author=}}</ref> Students Ana Cecilia Ramos Luis and Fernando Martinez, both 14 years old, and 24-year-old teacher Cecilia Cristina Solis suffered serious head injuries; 15-year-old Manuel Chavez suffered an arm injury.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.sdpnoticias.com/local/nuevo-leon/2017/01/18/difunden-nombres-de-heridos-por-disparos-en-colegio-americano| title=Spread of names of gunshot wounded at American College (Spanish)|work=[[SDP Noticias]]| date=18 January 2017| author=}}</ref> Guevara had psychological problems.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2017/01/18/gunfire-erupts-at-mexican-private-school-injuries-reported.html| title=15-year-old student shoots teacher, 3 classmates at American school in Mexico|work=[[Fox News]] (World)| date=2 March 2016| author=}}</ref> Teacher Cecilia Cristina Solis died on March 29, 2017, hours after being declared brain dead.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.milenio.com/region/muere-maestra-baleada-colegio_americano_noreste-milenio-monterrey_0_928707377.html| title=Muere Maestra baleada en Colegio Americano del Noreste (Spanish)|work=[[Milenio]]| date=29 March 2017| author=}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 20, 2017}}\n|[[West Liberty, Ohio]], US \n| Student, 17\n|\n| 1 injured\n| A student was shot and injured by another student at [[West Liberty-Salem High School]].\n|-\n|Januuary 27, 2017\n|[[Naperville, Illinois]], US\n| Unknown gunman\n| 1 dead\n| \n| 37-year-old son Matthew Lange, a popular associate professor of psychology at Lewis University, was shot and killed execution style in the driver\u2019s seat of his car while waiting to pick up his young son around 7 p.m. from a Polish heritage class at Scullen Middle School in Naperville. \n<ref>https://www.chicagotribune.com/suburbs/aurora-beacon-news/opinion/ct-abn-crosby-lange-murder-st-0126-20200124-6o3ksvjs6zginiglerny4g5mtq-story.html</ref><ref>https://www.chicagotribune.com/suburbs/aurora