=\"toccolours\" width=100%\n|{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Olavi Ahonen (basketball)|Olavi Ahonen]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Olli Ahvenniemi]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Joonas Cav\u00e9n]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|red|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Petri Heinonen]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|red|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Arvo Jantunen]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Pentti Kaivonen]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Mikko Koskinen (basketball)|Mikko Koskinen]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|red|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Jarmo Laitinen]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|red|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Antero Lehto]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|red|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Tero Minetti]] {{colorbull|red|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Antti Nikkil\u00e4]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|red|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Topias Palmi]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|red|d}}\n*{{flagicon|FIN|size=20px}} [[Kalevi Tuominen]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|URS|size=20px}}/{{flagicon|EST|size=20px}} [[Heino Enden]] {{colorbull|orange|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Ashante Johnson]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Carl Kilpatrick]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Edmund Lawrence (basketball)|Edmund Lawrence]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Kelvin Lewis]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Kenneth Lowe]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Ricky Minard]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}}/{{flagicon|GBR|size=20px}} [[Shawn Myers]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Marcus Norris]] {{colorbull|red|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[B.J. Raymond]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Eric Washington (basketball)|Eric Washington]] {{colorbull|green|d}}\n*{{flagicon|USA|size=20px}} [[Damon Williams]] {{colorbull|red|d}}{{colorbull|green|d}}\n}}\n----\n{{Refbegin}}\n;Notes\n:{{colorbull|orange|d}} Played at least one official international match for their national team at any time.\n:{{colorbull|red|d}} Set a club record or won an individual award while at the club.\n:{{colorbull|green|d}} To perform very successfully during period in the club or at later/previous stages of his career.\n{{refend}}\n|}\n\n== Women's team ==\nPyrint\u00f6's women's team currently plays in [[Women's Korisliiga]], the highest tier of basketball for women in [[Finland]], and has won eight Finnish titles and the Finnish Cup once. Among club's women's team, Pyrint\u00f6 has retired the jersey of [[Seija Leino]].\n\n== References ==\n<references/>\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|http://www.pyrinto.fi/}}\n\n{{Korisliiga}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tampereen Pyrinto (basketball)}}\n[[Category:Basketball teams in Finland]]\n[[Category:Basketball teams established in 1941]]\n[[Category:Sport in Tampere|Pyrinto]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Basketball club \n| color1 = White\n| color2 = #CC0000\n| name = Pyrint\u00f6\n| nickname =\n| logo = Tampereen Pyrint\u00f6 logo.svg\n| leagues= [[Korisliiga]]\n| founded ={{Start date and age|1941}}\n| history = '''Tampereen Pyrint\u00f6'''<br>(1941\u2013present)\n| arena = Pyynikin Palloiluhalli\n| location = [[Tampere]], [[Finland]]\n| colors = White and Red<br />{{color box|white}} {{color box|#CC0000}}\n| president = \n| coach = [[Sami Toiviainen]] \n| championships = '''3''' [[Korisliiga|Finnish Championships]]<br />'''2''' [[Finnish Basketball Cup|Finnish Cups]]\n| website = [http://www.pyrinto.fi/ www.pyrinto.fi]\n| h_body=CC0000|h_pattern_b=_basket_with_white|h_shorts=CC0000|h_pattern_s=_whitesides\n| a_body=FFFFFF|a_pattern_b=|a_shorts=FFFFFF|a_pattern_s=\n}}\n\n'''Tampereen Pyrint\u00f6''', more commonly referred to as shortly '''Pyrint\u00f6''', is a [[Finland|Finnish]] [[basketball]] team from [[Tampere]]. It is the basketball section of a [[Tampereen Pyrint\u00f6|club with the same name]]. Pyrint\u00f6's men's team plays in [[Korisliiga]], the highest tier of Finnish basketball.\n\nAfter 2010 Pyrint\u00f6 has participated in the [[EuroChallenge]] and the [[Baltic Basketball League]].\n\n== Achievements ==\n*'''[[Korisliiga]]: 3''' \n:'''Champions:''' 2010, 2011, 2014\n:''Runner-up:'' 1958, 1980, 1981, 2001, 2016\n:''Third\u2013place:'' 2009\n*'''[[Finnish Basketball Cup]]: 2'''\n:'''Champions''': 1969, 2013\n:''Runner-up:'' 2000, 2009, 2011\n*'''[[Baltic Basketball League]]'''\n:''Fourth\u2013place:'' 2014\n\n== Current roster ==\n{{Basketball roster nationality note}}\n{{Basketball roster header|team=Tampereen Pyrint\u00f6\n| color1 = #cc0000 | bg1 = white | color2 = white | bg2 = #cc0000 | wt = n | age = n }}\n<!-- list of players -->\n{{player3 | num =2  | nat = USA | name = Jaylon Tate       | pos = PG   | m = 1.90 }}\n{{player3 | num =3  | nat = USA | name = Kenneth Manigault | pos = G/F  | m = 1.96 }}\n{{player3 | num =4  | nat = FIN | name = Antero Lehto      | pos = PG   | m = 1.85 }}\n{{player3 | num =9  | nat = FIN | name = Lassi Kilpinen    | pos = PG   | m = 1.85 }}\n{{player3 | num =10 | nat = FIN | name = Osku Heinonen     | pos = G/F  | m = 1.94 }}\n{{player3 | num =11 | nat = FIN | name = Ville Haapoja     | pos = SF   | m = 2.00 }}\n{{player3 | num =13 | nat = FIN | name = Tuomas Flinck     | pos = PG   | m = 1.82 }}\n{{player3 | num =14 | nat = USA | name = Eron Harris       | pos = G    | m = 1.93 }}\n{{player3 | num =19 | nat = FIN | name = Tommi Luojus      | pos = G    | m = 1.84 }}\n{{player3 | num =21 | nat = FIN | name = Petri Heinonen    | pos = F/C  | m = 2.07 }}\n{{player3 | num =31 | nat = FIN | name 